        ('stretching', '', 'static', 'exercisesListImg\The_Straddle\0.jpg', 'exercisesListImg\The_Straddle\1.jpg', ' Begin in a seated, upright position. Start by extending your legs in front of you in a V.; With your hands on the floor, lean forward as far as possible. Hold for 10 to 20 seconds.', 'beginner', '', 'The Straddle', 'hamstrings', 'adductors;calves'),
